{"tid":1716397,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中大強烈譴責校園連串衝突暴力及違法行為","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:12:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfc72f7f2421bc2f59962f5d3a98a80f0b133dd","tid":1716397,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"中文大學發表聲明，對昨日校園發生的連串衝突、暴力及違法行為深表遺憾，並予以強烈譴責。<br />\n發言人說，校長及高層人員屢次嘗試作出調停及談判，但雙方持續對峙，過程中，在場人士持續投擲汽油彈及攻擊物品等，警方亦多次發射催淚彈及橡膠彈等，導致校內多人受傷，大學深表遺憾及歉意。<br />\n中大又說，有責任保障校園內所有人員及學生安全，絕不容許任何形式的暴力或危害他人安全的行為，任何人士如果意圖利用校園作出違法或暴力行為，大學必須按照既定守則及法例，維護校園及學生職員安全。<br />\n大學呼籲職員、學生及各界人士，給予大學時間及空間，讓大學盡快恢復秩序及安寧。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491947-20191113.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491947-20191113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QoDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=4e833dcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491947-20191113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c2e9a882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491947-20191113.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e3c899a2337b1f1fac78ac8ea8c33e157f863b85","tid":1716397,"uid":163149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"大學呼籲<span style=\"color: red;\">職員、學生及各界人士</span>，給予大學時間及空間，讓大學盡快恢復秩序及安寧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑人問號， 邊個搞事都未分清楚"},{"pid":"68f474fe6b27f87675928a0c3744352d99e08068","tid":1716397,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"是但啦，無用"},{"pid":"b12bd5dd6da707f41887774ae4f8c2d5c8c9f9a0","tid":1716397,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:38:36.000Z","msg":"兩班政見不同學生打鬥 ?"},{"pid":"fb8acec17638f2f90ae57917fceba62b267033e2","tid":1716397,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r